@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false

actor User

component "Browser UI\n(Radio Buttons)" as UI
component "Razor View\nBBInvForm.cshtml" as View
component "Resource Files\nInvResource(.resx)" as Resx
component "CSS\n(form-check / display rules)" as CSS
component "JavaScript\nBBInvForm.js" as JS
component "jQuery\n+ Validation" as JQuery

User --> UI : selects radio option

View --> UI : renders HTML\n(ids, names, inputs)
Resx --> View : localized strings\n(question + labels)
CSS --> UI : visibility & layout\n(display: none/block)

UI --> JS : change event\n(input[type=radio])
JS --> JQuery : DOM queries\n& validation
JS --> UI : show/hide sections\n(enable/disable submit
JS --> JS : checkEntireForm()

note right of JS
Uses selectors like:
#divNewScorecardOrNo
input[name=optradioOldScorecard]
#divDisclaimerData
end note

@enduml